By: St Thomas Aquinas
---
Those who obtain ultimate happiness from the divine vision never fall away
from it. Because whatever at one time is, and at another time is not, is
measured by time. ... Now the vision in question ... is not in time but in
eternity. Therefore no one, having once become partaker thereof, can lose it.
